Charles Leonard Steel Services
Charles Leonard Steel Services (CLSS) is a full-service miscellaneous metals fabricator and erector specializing in steel stairs, railings, structural steel, grating, decks, and ladders.

Resource Corporation of America specializes in converting hospitals' at-risk dollars into revenue, focusing on third-party eligibility solutions. With over 30 years of experience, they have achieved a 93% certification success rate and have managed more than two billion dollars in patient account charges. Their services are aimed at hospitals navigating complex healthcare policies and regulatory changes. The company stands as a trusted partner for healthcare leaders seeking to optimize revenue amid evolving Medicaid reforms. The company headquarters is located in 1120 Marina Bay Dr, Kemah, TX 77565, United States. 201-500 Employees

L'Epi du Rouergue is a bakery and pastry shop located in the Aveyron region, operating 12 stores across the Tarn and Aveyron departments and participating in over 80 markets in the South-West of France. The company specializes in a variety of handmade products including breads, pastries, cakes, sandwiches, and traditional Aveyron specialties like fouace. With a commitment to freshness, their products are made without freezing, ensuring high-quality offerings for their customers. Founded in 1973 by a group of local bakers, L'Epi du Rouergue has grown to employ around 250 staff members and offers online ordering with home delivery options

SapLog specializes in national and international transport services, offering full truckload (FTL) and less-than-truckload (LTL) shipping solutions across Italy and Europe. The company provides dedicated express transport for urgent requests and a range of accessory services to enhance efficiency. With a modern fleet of vehicles that adhere to Euro 6 standards, SapLog ensures safe and environmentally friendly transportation. Their intended clients include businesses requiring reliable logistics solutions for their goods.
